# climate/ (Crisis & Canopy) is tracked and built into dist/canopyandcrisis.
# Its own climate/.gitignore excludes raw datasets; the global node_modules/dist
# rules above also apply inside it; the app's runtime data in
# climate/toronto-app/public/data/ is intentionally committed. Keep the heavy
# local Python venv out regardless of how git descends into the folder:
climate/venv/
